之前有班人係咁叫義士返香港受審, 都ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既<br />\n<br />\n根本就係殖民地法官, 幫手砌生豬肉</blockquote><br />\n上面嗰班係陶君行來"},{"pid":"ea5a34eed361e7d09864ed3eb22fa8cf663e2acb","tid":442653,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最動罪本身就包埋放火行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雙重定罪，同支那國仲有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班支那賤種五毛死全家啦</blockquote><br />\n按《公安條例》第19條，若集結按《公安條例》第18條被定為非法集結，而非法集結的人中的任何一人，作出了破壞社會安寧的行為，非法集結就會變成暴動，而所有集結的人就是集結暴動。參與暴動的人即犯暴動罪。</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母閪5毛收聲"},{"pid":"aa8b0052a1d5744fd3eadf01419f3e2dc13c6b3b","tid":442653,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:21:14.000Z","msg":"幫手砌生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e2ebfca49eedc265d19f0d0a7d8d72f8df13a9","tid":442653,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"殺無赦"},{"pid":"23e34d21a2c611a91b0bb6f3c14b7a9c29895d28","tid":442653,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"法官做埋主控嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29320d203bfe25b823bbb996ceea13802cd8bae","tid":442653,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁都得"},{"pid":"35a71603936b9d9ddf2fb37ec62f3f0132d51ee8","tid":442653,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:42:23.000Z","msg":"咁不如律政司摺咗佢<br />\n以後法官自己提控自已審埋好唔好？<br />\n香港根本已經冇法治可言<br />\n連法官都要愛國"},{"pid":"c3017d7445cfc652c293b504d19cf4acb3a65608","tid":442653,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52f3e43784d319d585bb3e9797fdd88a51b7a51","tid":442653,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"郭文貴接受專訪時說國安、公安早已滲透在香港各處，這一點絕對可信。<span style=\"color: red;\">1949年解放前後，中共除了滲透黨員在香港，也一直在香港培養黨員。</span>傳聞梁振英是地下黨員，大家都不知道真假；但看他處理異己分子的手法，絕對是阿爺那一套，否則他也不可能官至國家領導。香港的共產黨員絕對不少，「六七暴動」時已經有六、七萬參與者。當時香港是英國殖民地，已經有那麼多黨員滲透了；回歸後更名正言順每天150人，20年來已經有超過一百萬大陸人來了香港。算這一百多萬新移民中，只有10%是中共派來的，已經是十多萬人，數量比「六七暴動」人數多得多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/3680/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8-3680/%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B9%8B%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%8D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F3680%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%25BB%25A8-3680%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25AE%2596%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%25B0%25E3%2580%258D%25E2%2580%2594%25E2%2580%2594%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=SqI5g1WaY6r%2Fyy9H4DuS9CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b94c02a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/3680/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8-3680/%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B9%8B%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%8D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n唔計每日150人，1949-1997期間，共匪已經係香港，不斷收篇各種各類人入黨。<br />\n<br />\n根據以上推測，唔難明點解香港有權有勢既，越嚟越紅。以前專業形象只係掩飾，當黨覺得冇需要，就叫你做返自己就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8e1148f2d1fcf3065fc666796d7d6680ab6a2f","tid":442653,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfcd1fd87e8ec153fc7d53f1e944bd59bd4c202f","tid":442653,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"公民抗命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceef09261abc0f34428a1cf68e6c061f7b93cee9","tid":442653,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"有撚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce81e51e7ab077cb723b83058f3f949d63ca9a1","tid":442653,"uid":89036,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"個官真黃絲黎架<br />\n做到咁條友咪可以上訴推翻判決囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83da7a3994c8cf15f73942077097c91bc636ab7d","tid":442653,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"乜法官可以做埋檢控果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辯方要求傳開槍黑警上庭又唔比，淨係信哂控方d「可靠證人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}